Package: gistillery
Type: Package
Title: Upload Code to Github Gists and Take Code Screenshots via Carbon
Version: 0.2.5
Author: Thomas Mock
Maintainer: Thomas Mock <j.thomasmock@gmail.com>
Description: Easily upload code to Github Gists from local files, the clipboard, or even a reprex.
    Quickly take customized and beautiful screenshots of your code from Carbon.
